  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Puzzle Adventure That’s as Cozy as a Warm Cup of Tea!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Ringo’s Roundup</i>, you join <strong>Ringo, the fluffiest postbunny in town</strong>, on his <strong>mail delivery adventure</strong>! But there’s a twist—Ringo <strong>doesn’t control his car directly</strong>. Instead, YOU <strong>plan his route</strong> by carefully placing <strong>Effect Tiles</strong> on the road.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is a charming <strong>pathfinding puzzle</strong>, where your goal is to <strong>collect all the envelopes in the right order and drop them off at the mailbox</strong>. But be careful! The road is full of twists, turns, and obstacles, and you’ll need to <strong>experiment, strategize, and adapt</strong> to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/f681ecb777e99da071e94ddd056afd9d.poster.avif?t=1753886911\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/f681ecb777e99da071e94ddd056afd9d.webm?t=1753886911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/f681ecb777e99da071e94ddd056afd9d.mp4?t=1753886911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Simple Mechanics, Endless Possibilities!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ringo’s Roundup</i> starts off easy, but as you progress, you’ll discover <strong>unexpected depth</strong> in its puzzle mechanics! Each <strong>Effect Tile</strong> has a unique function, and when combined, they create <strong>exciting new challenges</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/e78863eab87b21444eee9269fe757bd0.poster.avif?t=1753886911\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/e78863eab87b21444eee9269fe757bd0.webm?t=1753886911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/e78863eab87b21444eee9269fe757bd0.mp4?t=1753886911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 <strong>JUMP</strong> – Bounce over obstacles and tricky terrain!<br>🔮 <strong>PORTALS</strong> – Teleport across the level for creative solutions!<br>🧲 <strong>MAGNETS</strong> – Push or pull objects to clear the way!<br>🛑 <strong>Direction Tiles</strong> – Control turns and set the perfect path!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every puzzle has <strong>multiple solutions</strong>, rewarding both careful planning and playful experimentation. No two players will find the same path—so <strong>challenge yourself to discover the smartest, most creative routes!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/cc02cffb3f057fa6fd52e1dac51be847.poster.avif?t=1753886911\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/cc02cffb3f057fa6fd52e1dac51be847.webm?t=1753886911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/cc02cffb3f057fa6fd52e1dac51be847.mp4?t=1753886911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why You’ll Love Ringo’s Roundup</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>100 handcrafted levels</strong> with carefully designed puzzles<br>✔️ <strong>Chill, stress-free gameplay</strong> – No timers, no pressure!<br>✔️ <strong>Multiple solutions for many levels</strong> – Play your way!<br>✔️ <strong>Adorable customization</strong> – Unlock new car colors for Ringo!<br>✔️ <strong>A cozy, colorful world</strong> full of charm and personality<br>✔️ <strong>A cute bunny postman</strong> on a wholesome journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>Perfect for puzzle lovers, cozy gamers, and anyone looking for a charming, relaxing experience.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hop in, start planning, and <strong>help Ringo deliver the mail in the most delightful way possible!</strong> 🐰📬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/c1dca5a95e2d161d558e764c1c760789.poster.avif?t=1753886911\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/c1dca5a95e2d161d558e764c1c760789.webm?t=1753886911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769290/extras/c1dca5a95e2d161d558e764c1c760789.mp4?t=1753886911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
